<small class="form-text text-muted">
    <b>About: </b>This demo simulates the various sports (NFL, Basketball) outcomes (playoffs, championships won) using actual league structure.
</small>
<small class="form-text text-muted">
    The purpose of the demo is to highlight that Blazor WebAssembly architectures can run monte carlo simulations directly on the web client to perform analytical analysis.
    Analytically, this demo allows you to compare the probability of making the playoffs or winning a championship by chance with different league & playoff structures.
</small>
